# make copy of the raw DB
df19_init = df19.copy()
df20_init = df20.copy()

# Shifted data with all values
df19["Datetime"] = pd.to_datetime(df19.index + timedelta(days=365-1))
df19.set_index('Datetime', inplace=True)
dfHDD19["Datetime"] = pd.to_datetime(dfHDD19.index + timedelta(days=365-1+7))
dfHDD19.set_index('Datetime', inplace=True)
dfHDD20["Datetime"] = pd.to_datetime(dfHDD20.index + timedelta(days=7))
dfHDD20.set_index('Datetime', inplace=True)

df20["Datetime"] = pd.to_datetime(df20.index)
df20.set_index('Datetime', inplace=True)
alldf = df19[['LOAD19','TEMP19','PEN19']]
alldf = alldf.merge(df20[['LOAD20','TEMP20','PEN20']], left_index=True, right_index=True)
# Focus on specific area
alldf = alldf[(alldf.index.weekofyear >= 10) & (alldf.index.weekofyear <= 17)]
dfHDD19 = dfHDD19[(dfHDD19.index.weekofyear >= 10) & (dfHDD19.index.weekofyear <= 17)]
dfHDD20 = dfHDD20[(dfHDD20.index.weekofyear >= 10) & (dfHDD20.index.weekofyear <= 17)]

allHDD = dfHDD20
allHDD.rename(columns={'HDD': 'HDD20'}, inplace=True)
allHDD['HDD19'] = dfHDD19['HDD']
allHDD['HDDDIFF'] = allHDD['HDD20'] - allHDD['HDD19']

# Shifted data without weekends and other holidays only weeks 12 to 17
removelist = ['2019-03-02', '2020-03-25','2020-04-01','2020-04-17',
              '2020-04-20','2019-03-11','2019-03-25','2019-04-01',
              '2019-04-26','2019-04-29']
df19wd = df19_init[[d.date() not in pd.to_datetime(removelist) for d in df19_init.index]]
df19wd = df19wd[ (df19wd.index.weekofyear >= 12) & (df19wd.index.weekofyear <= 17) & (df19wd.index.weekday < 5) ]
df20wd = df20_init[[d.date() not in pd.to_datetime(removelist) for d in df20_init.index]]
df20wd = df20wd[ (df20wd.index.weekofyear >= 12) & (df20wd.index.weekofyear <= 17) & (df20wd.index.weekday < 5) ]

import numpy as np
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler

df_uci_init = alldf.copy(deep=True)
df_uci_init = df_uci_init[ (alldf.index.weekday < 5) ]
df_uci_init = df_uci_init.drop(['PEN19','TEMP19','PEN20','TEMP20'], axis=1)
years = ['LOAD19','LOAD20']
#print(df19wd,df20wd)
dbs = [df19wd.drop(['CAP','WIND','PV','CONV','PEN19','TEMP19'], axis=1), 
       df20wd.drop(['CAP','WIND','PV','CONV','PEN20','TEMP20'], axis=1)]
first = True
for yr, df_uci  in zip(years,dbs):
    
    df_uci = df_uci.replace('?', np.nan)
    df_uci = df_uci.astype(np.float).fillna(method='bfill')

    df_uci_hourly = df_uci.resample('H').mean()
    df_uci_hourly['hour'] = df_uci_hourly.index.hour
    df_uci_hourly.index = df_uci_hourly.index.date

    df_uci_pivot = df_uci_hourly.pivot(columns='hour')
    df_uci_pivot = df_uci_pivot.dropna()

    X = df_uci_pivot.values.copy()

    # Very important to scale!
    sc = MinMaxScaler()
    X = sc.fit_transform(X)
    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=1)
    cluster_found = kmeans.fit_predict(X)
    cluster_found_sr = pd.Series(cluster_found, name='cluster')
    df_uci_pivot = df_uci_pivot.set_index(cluster_found_sr, append=True )

    cluster_values = sorted(df_uci_pivot.index.get_level_values('cluster').unique())
    
    if first:
        myfig = df_uci_pivot.xs(0, level=1).median().droplevel(level=0).iplot(asFigure = True)
        myfig.update_traces(name=yr,mode='lines',line=dict(width=1.5))
        first = False
    else:
        myfig.add_trace(go.Scatter(x=df_uci_pivot.xs(0, level=1).median().index.droplevel(level=0),y=df_uci_pivot.xs(0, level=1).median().values, mode='lines',name=yr,line=dict(width=1.5,color=cf.colors.hex_to_rgb('blue'))))

myfig.update_layout(title='. 5:          16 -26 ',
                   xaxis_title='',
                   yaxis_title='MW',
                   xaxis = dict(tickmode = 'linear',
                        tick0 = 0, dtick = 2), showlegend=True)
if inPNG:
    myfig.write_image("images/fig5.png",height = imheight, width = imwidth, scale = imscale)
    display(Image("images/fig5.png"))
else:
    myfig.show()
